Business Brief -- Burnham Pacific Properties Inc.:
   Shareholders Approve Plan
   To Buy Management Firm
Under the plan, Burnham Pacific agreed to exchange 80,000
shares of its stock for all of the stock outstanding of its
management company, Burnham Investment Group Inc., a unit of
privately owned John Burnham  Co. Prior to the trust's
conversion in 1987 to a corporation from a limited
partnership, Burnham Investment Group was the partnership's
general partner.